&lt;li&gt;Excellent verbal and written communication/presentation skills with a strong focus on customer interaction, customer service, and presentation.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A motivated self-starter with the capability to operate on their own with little direction and/or monitoring.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Capability to help deliver quality business solutions within restricted timelines while appropriately communicating/escalating risks, issues, or constraints as necessary to business and/or IT management.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to elicit cooperation from a wide variety of sources, including upper management, business partners, and other departments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability

