&lt;li&gt;Knowledge in NERC, ERCOT, WECC, CAISO, PJM, and SPP regulations and requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to coordinate multiple activities and ensure safety, compliance, quality, and schedule adherence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to take direction, identify problems, analyze root cause, and develop solutions in collaboration with others.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work well with others during stressful situations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt

